Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.46,0:03:18.13,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,送到老师家的书包也是由「他人」送来的么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.51,0:03:22.13,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,是他人  对我来说
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.56,0:03:27.72,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,真可爱…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.22,0:03:31.06,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,您今天心情不错呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.69,0:03:33.77,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.27,0:03:36.57,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,购买不是义务而是权利吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.19,0:03:39.86,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,要是漫画不是让读者想着「买」
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.15,0:03:43.07,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,而是让读者想着「请让我买」就好了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.78,0:03:45.49,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,就是这个
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.78,0:03:48.29,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,真是温柔的世界呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.12,0:03:50.37,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,开  开玩笑的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.58,0:03:53.50,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,这种像神一样的读者怎么可能存在
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.17,0:03:54.75,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,确实
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.42,0:03:59.09,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,想要让读者也成为温柔世界的居民的话
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.76,0:04:04.01,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我们创作方得率先成为温柔世界的居民才行
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.85,0:04:07.80,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我擦我擦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.56,0:04:10.81,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我有幸能使用着橡皮擦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.81,0:04:12.85,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我网我网
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.85,0:04:17.11,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我有幸能画着麻烦的网格
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.77,0:04:21.78,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我有幸能画着复杂的俯角街道背景
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.44,0:04:25.82,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,如何  成为温柔世界的居民后的心情
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.49,0:04:28.62,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,非常清爽的感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.12,0:04:31.62,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,为啥感觉社畜感这么重
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.91,0:04:36.29,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,是的  我们有幸能登上主流周刊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.58,0:04:38.79,kakushigoto tip,,0,0,0,,{\an8}温柔
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.63,0:04:37.58,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,有幸
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.84,0:04:43.22,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,是的是的  老实说本想让他再加把劲的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.76,0:04:46.64,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,难得让他登上主流周刊了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.18,0:04:52.02,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,就是你吗  温柔世界的破坏者
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.22,0:04:53.43,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,突然怎么了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.77,0:04:56.81,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,你就没有对他人的感激之情吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.77,0:05:00.86,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,当然有的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.69,0:05:03.53,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,特别是对全国的书店
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.94,0:05:06.91,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我都抱着一腔感谢他们让我们发售的感激之情
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.70,0:05:10.08,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,这确实很重要
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.49,0:05:11.95,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,是的  所以呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.45,0:05:14.66,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,这是啥
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.24,0:05:17.33,kakushigoto tip,,0,0,0,,注：源自三洋堂  Animate  有隣堂  喜久屋书店  虎穴  Melonbooks
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.50,0:05:17.96,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,不同书店特典插画卡片二十张
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.88,0:05:19.63,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,二十…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.84,0:05:26.05,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,身为温柔世界的居民真是辛苦啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.34,0:05:30.26,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,最近我家小孩完全不听我话
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.85,0:05:31.97,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我家也是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.39,0:05:35.60,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,明明小孩只要听家长的话就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.14,0:05:38.85,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,也不想想是谁在辛苦养育他们
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.19,0:05:41.61,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,不是这样的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.77,0:05:47.03,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,至少我是  有幸能够抚养孩子的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.90,0:05:48.70,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,欢迎回来
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.53,0:05:53.29,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.12,0:05:58.79,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,工作真开心  工作真开心
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.96,0:06:06.46,kakushigoto tip,,0,0,0,,{\an8}工作真开心  工作真开心
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.71,0:06:01.21,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,那是怎么了…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.84,0:06:06.13,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,温柔世界的居民接了太多的工作快要爆炸了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.88,0:06:08.09,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,这几天…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.88,0:06:17.48,kakushigoto in 3 - heng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,0)\c&H585664&\pos(1364.8,433.2)}赠品用色纸10张（彩色）
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.09,0:06:11.34,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,好的  当然了  请让我画
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.89,0:06:17.48,kakushigoto in 3 - heng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,0)\c&H515160&\pos(688,433.6)}尻名老师fanbook  商稿4格8页
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.89,0:06:17.48,kakushigoto tip,,0,0,0,,注：源自久米田康治的好友椎名高志
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.14,0:06:14.39,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,好的  当然了  请让我画
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.02,0:06:17.48,kakushigoto in 3 - heng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,0)\c&H545161&\pos(225.2,431.2)}动画的ed卡
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.18,0:06:17.39,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,好的  当然了  请让我画
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.89,0:06:19.64,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,这日程表是怎么回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.23,0:06:22.86,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,接到工作  不是件很值得感激的事情吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.86,0:06:25.94,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,老师变了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.40,0:06:28.53,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,真的  这都成社畜了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.99,0:06:30.99,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,不  漫画家都是个体户
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.53,0:06:34.24,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,也就是说现在的老师不是社畜
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.62,0:06:35.70,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,而是漫畜
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.37,0:06:44.25,kakushigoto tip,,0,0,0,,{\an8}是漫畜
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.50,0:06:40.96,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,这个创造了新的词语后满足的样子是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.96,0:06:44.13,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,该说是酿成了成就感还是兴奋感总之快停下啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.84,0:06:47.51,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,这是漫画家最近在画漫画以外
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.51,0:06:49.47,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,也得做各种各样的事情的一个时代
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.76,0:06:52.05,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,漫畜化的进展越来越深了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.51,0:06:53.89,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,比如这个签售会什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.18,0:06:55.93,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,签售会？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.60,0:06:57.22,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,谁的？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.43,0:06:58.48,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,谁的…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.89,0:07:00.85,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,不是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.23,0:07:03.15,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,在混乱之中接下了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.36,0:07:04.98,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,你这漫畜啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.19,0:07:06.65,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,漫畜就是您自己
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.90,0:07:08.15,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,在人们面前露脸
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.28,0:07:09.74,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,要是被姬发现了该怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.99,0:07:11.20,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,得赶快拒绝
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.57,0:07:13.45,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,要取消已经不可能了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.78,0:07:15.49,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,在网上都发过公告了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.29,0:07:20.79,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,而且还是星期天  这天要和姬一起…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.37,0:07:22.96,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我很期待星期天呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.67,0:07:26.25,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,终于预约到KidZanira了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.34,0:07:29.21,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,KidZanira？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.84,0:07:31.80,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,是在小孩里很有人气的主题公园
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.26,0:07:31.80,kakushigoto tip,,0,0,0,,注：源自Kidzania家庭教育娱乐中心游乐园
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.30,0:07:36.81,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,能体验各种职业  要预约到也很难哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.47,0:07:38.26,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,先走了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.60,0:07:39.64,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.14,0:07:45.94,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,可是  为什么老师他突然就变为那样的好人了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.69,0:07:47.90,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,难道发生过什么吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.53,0:07:49.73,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,肯定是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.16,0:07:58.83,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,差不多也该停止送书包了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.12,0:08:03.08,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,让我每年该怎么说明才好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.08,0:08:06.79,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,还是怀恨在心么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.84,0:08:10.88,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,说没有怀恨在心也是骗人的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.92,0:08:13.38,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,你也成为家长了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.88,0:08:16.59,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,也稍微体会到一些我这边的心情了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.10,0:08:23.64,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,如果在将来  姬带回来的结婚对象
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.10,0:08:26.98,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,是个在画名叫「鸡鸡复鸡鸡」漫画的男人的话
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.77,0:08:29.15,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,你能允许么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.52,0:08:31.15,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,怎么可能会允许
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.28,0:08:34.07,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.32,0:08:35.99,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,再会了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.50,0:08:43.12,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,确实…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.41,0:08:46.42,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我绝不可能把姬托付给
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.75,0:08:47.96,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,在画我这种漫画的男人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.50,0:08:51.30,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,绝对不可能
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.59,0:08:52.42,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,自我矛盾
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.51,0:08:58.43,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,在画「鸡鸡复鸡鸡」这种漫画的家伙签名啥的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.76,0:08:59.89,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,有谁会想要
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.97,0:09:04.39,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,果然发生了什么导致失去自信了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.93,0:09:08.06,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,好人化是丧失自信的负面表现么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.48,0:09:10.11,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,反正签售会谁都不会来的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.40,0:09:11.73,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我要陪姬去玩了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.03,0:09:13.49,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,这可不能…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.78,0:09:20.16,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,这说不定  两边都可以兼顾哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.08,0:09:28.71,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,再往前面大人不可进入了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.50,0:09:30.46,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我出发了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.00,0:09:32.17,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,玩开心点
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.84,0:09:38.30,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,原来如此  这么一回事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.68,0:09:39.72,kakushigoto in,,0,0,0,,{\fad(700,0)\bord0\pos(787.2,300.8)\c&HFFFFFF&}几天前
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.93,0:09:43.39,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,怎么才能同时兼顾KidZanira和签售会啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.77,0:09:47.89,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,在KidZanira基本上大人都只是在等候室里看着孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.90,0:09:51.27,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,在这期间举行签售会就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.73,0:09:55.78,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,看  签售会会场的书店在同一栋建筑里的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.27,0:09:58.57,kakushigoto tip,,0,0,0,,注：书店名源自纪伊国屋书店
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.19,0:09:57.45,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,超幸运的呀
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.74,0:09:58.49,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,确实
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.74,0:10:00.16,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我说这也太近了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.03,0:10:03.03,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,要是发生点什么情况偶遇了…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.37,0:10:05.20,kakushigoto in 7,,0,0,0,,{\bord2\c&HB8A6C7&\pos(668.8,62.8)}黄段子漫画家签售会
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.79,0:10:04.62,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,爸爸？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.25,0:10:06.16,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,不行不行不行不行
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.25,0:10:07.41,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,绝对不行
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.75,0:10:09.50,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,但是也只能硬着头皮上了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.75,0:10:11.33,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,大家都会帮忙的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.75,0:10:14.30,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,老师
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.09,0:10:15.88,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,这边这边
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.38,0:10:20.13,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,签名程度的话这身打扮也能画的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.72,0:10:21.39,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,当然
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.22,0:10:23.10,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,画不出来
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.52,0:10:29.19,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,在那拐角转过去的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.98,0:10:33.19,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,果然我还是回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.27,0:10:34.73,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,怎么了啊突然
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.02,0:10:36.78,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,反正谁都不会来的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.90,0:10:39.07,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,相当缺乏自信呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.45,0:10:41.49,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,没事的  会来很多人的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.49,0:10:42.37,kakushigoto in 3 - heng,,0,0,0,,{\pos(355.2,755.2)\c&H393B48&}毫无根据
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.53,0:10:43.99,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,好啦搞快点
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.03,0:10:45.12,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,不行不行不行不行
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.24,0:10:46.37,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,快住手
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.79,0:10:49.83,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.04,0:10:51.12,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,排成长队了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.88,0:10:53.50,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,所以我都说了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.88,0:10:56.46,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,会来很多人的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.92,0:11:01.93,kakushigoto in 7,,0,0,0,,{\bord2\pos(803.6,21.2)\org(970,21.2)\frx348\fry0}路堤君  签售会
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.92,0:11:01.93,kakushigoto in 7,,0,0,0,,{\bord2\fs40\pos(1150.4,260.8)\org(1270.4,257.6)\frx352\fry4}写真集发售纪念
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.38,0:10:59.88,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,路堤
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.14,0:11:04.18,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,是当地吉祥物的…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.55,0:11:05.72,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,签售会
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.23,0:11:12.94,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,还挺难的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.69,0:11:17.19,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,为什么是我来担任监护人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.86,0:11:20.57,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,您家的孩子也在做糕点师吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.99,0:11:25.53,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我只是看着小女孩  我的孩子…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.12,0:11:30.29,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,只是看别人家的小孩  会被当作是可疑人士的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.71,0:11:32.54,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,是…是女儿
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.08,0:11:34.67,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,那个齐刘海的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.63,0:11:37.17,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,今天是爸爸一个人来吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.67,0:11:40.26,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我想想  母亲因为工作关系…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.72,0:11:43.43,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,星期天工作什么的真是辛苦呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.89,0:11:44.80,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,妻子她…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.55,0:11:46.97,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,是国际航线的空姐
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.14,0:11:48.64,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,现在正在飞海外的航班上
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.56,0:11:50.14,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,换人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.56,0:11:51.56,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,抱歉  给你这个
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.60,0:11:56.61,kakushigoto in,,0,0,0,,{\pos(286,138)\c&H42464F&}丈夫
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.60,0:11:56.61,kakushigoto in,,0,0,0,,{\pos(86,650)\c&H42464F&}女儿
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.60,0:11:56.61,kakushigoto in,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1222,134)\c&H42464F&}妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.60,0:11:54.48,kakushigoto in 10 - zong,,0,0,0,,{\frz269.1\c&H4F5B6D&\fs75\pos(1086,412)}身高175cm
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.60,0:11:56.61,kakushigoto in,,0,0,0,,{\fs60\pos(1400,290)\c&H4F5B6D&}国际航班空姐（德航）
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.60,0:11:56.61,kakushigoto in,,0,0,0,,{\fs65\c&H4F5B6D&\pos(1600,360)}IQ 200
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.60,0:11:53.10,kakushigoto in,,0,0,0,,{\fs60\c&H4F5B6D&\pos(1340,550)}原小平市选美小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.60,0:11:53.10,kakushigoto in,,0,0,0,,{\fs60\c&H4F5B6D&\pos(1536,688)}托业860分
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.60,0:11:53.10,kakushigoto in,,0,0,0,,{\fs60\c&H4F5B6D&\pos(1198,834)}武将的后裔（故意没说是谁）
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.60,0:11:53.10,kakushigoto in,,0,0,0,,{\fs60\c&H4F5B6D&\pos(1208,992)}cookpad上粉丝超过1万人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.35,0:11:54.23,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,这什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.69,0:11:56.48,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,姬妈妈的角色设定图
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.86,0:11:59.23,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,你这种设定漫画里都行不通啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.07,0:12:01.69,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,哎呀  您是？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.03,0:12:04.74,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,妻子现在应该在航班上
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.20,0:12:08.16,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我是…那孩子的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.29,0:12:09.95,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.08,0:12:13.29,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我15岁了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.67,0:12:18.67,kakushigoto in 6,,0,0,0,,{\bord3\pos(550,28)\c&H585C5E&}「风之紧身裤」后藤可久士老师签售会
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.54,0:12:18.38,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,你看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.00,0:12:19.80,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,一个人都没
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.46,0:12:23.17,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,那现在离开场还有一小时当然啦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.84,0:12:27.89,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,而且参加者都是提前抽签中抽出的限定100位
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.89,0:12:31.43,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,这种手段就是让别人觉得我是人气作家
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.60,0:12:33.23,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,然后将名额私下转卖
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.52,0:12:36.73,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,肯定是你们知道我没什么人气但又不好开口
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.27,0:12:38.61,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我知道您现在很焦虑
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.19,0:12:40.78,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,但其实最焦虑的是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.24,0:12:43.61,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,书店的工作人员们
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.15,0:12:45.36,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,不是你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.11,0:12:47.41,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,书店的工作人员们
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.57,0:12:49.95,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,他们可是拼尽了全力不让作家蒙羞
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.58,0:12:52.16,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,甚至是到了危急时刻
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.16,0:12:54.00,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,他们可以换成便装然后来排队
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.41,0:12:55.75,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我就知道是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.58,0:12:59.71,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,你们的脸我记住了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.21,0:13:02.21,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,如果让我看到你们在排队的话
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.59,0:13:03.38,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我就哭给你们看
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.30,0:13:06.97,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,看来又来了一位让人头疼的作家
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.40,0:13:20.06,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,能够体验这么多职业啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.02,0:13:23.07,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,请容许我再提醒一遍
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.53,0:13:25.45,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,签售会是一场和时间赛跑的比赛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.03,0:13:27.45,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,如果您要画角色的话
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.57,0:13:29.03,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,每个人画一个就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.66,0:13:31.66,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,还有  为了防止签名转卖
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.87,0:13:33.54,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,请一定要写上粉丝名字
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.45,0:13:36.29,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,那么我们就开始吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.75,0:13:39.38,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,排队的托儿准备好了就请开始吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.29,0:13:43.17,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,请各位粉丝进场
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.76,0:13:45.76,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,麻烦您了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.72,0:13:48.93,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我是老师您的忠实粉丝
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.22,0:13:51.30,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,这哪是托儿啊  完全就是自己人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.76,0:13:55.35,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,真就除了这么明显的托儿以外就找不到人了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.56,0:13:58.23,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我可是正经地参加了抽签然后被选中的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.56,0:13:59.60,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,请您签名
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.61,0:14:02.52,kakushigoto tip,,0,0,0,,{\an8}致一子小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.65,0:14:02.23,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,给
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.94,0:14:04.57,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,太谢谢您了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.03,0:14:07.28,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,麻烦您了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.32,0:14:09.57,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,好像没见过这人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.82,0:14:11.37,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,可能是真正的粉丝
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.91,0:14:14.79,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,小桃  你来了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.62,0:14:17.46,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我被选中了  真是太幸运了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.46,0:14:19.92,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,你要是给我说一声  我就去拜托老师给你一张签名的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.96,0:14:21.83,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,那样也太不好意思了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.54,0:14:23.29,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,给您
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.92,0:14:25.09,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,太谢谢您了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.80,0:14:27.76,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,刚才那女生  是我的大学朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.01,0:14:29.88,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,她好久以前就是老师的忠实粉丝
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.22,0:14:31.47,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,你以为我会信？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.05,0:14:32.85,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,说的也是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.64,0:14:34.39,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,真是太惨了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.97,0:14:36.27,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,像这样的关怀方式
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.60,0:14:38.18,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,明明对谁都没有好处
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.19,0:14:40.14,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,可是这群家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.35,0:14:43.86,kakushigoto tip,,0,0,0,,{\an8}呵呵  呵呵
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.52,0:14:43.52,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,他们被强迫参与排队  为什么看上去还这么高兴
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.57,0:14:45.86,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我知道了  这群家伙是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.57,0:14:47.40,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,您是打工的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.95,0:14:50.49,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,您居然知道啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.74,0:14:51.49,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我的确是个打工的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.91,0:14:52.87,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,果然是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.03,0:14:53.62,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,深夜的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.66,0:14:56.29,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我一边在便利店打工一边朝着成为漫画家努力着
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.37,0:14:57.12,kakushigoto in 6,,0,0,0,,{\pos(462,818)\c&H4A4447&}没在听
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.04,0:14:59.37,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,麻烦您了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.08,0:15:01.37,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,您也是打工的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.83,0:15:02.92,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,不是  我是临时工
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.33,0:15:06.21,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,居然明显到了直接说自己是临时工的这种地步
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.34,0:15:08.21,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,总是升不到正式员工
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.26,0:15:09.01,kakushigoto in 6,,0,0,0,,{\c&H4A4447&\pos(430,786)}没在听
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.13,0:15:11.43,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,您的时薪是多少
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.93,0:15:16.56,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我住在乡下  时薪大概是850日元左右
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.52,0:15:19.43,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,但是他们会为我报销路费
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.35,0:15:21.14,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.02,0:15:24.94,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,老师  上午的50名已经结束了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.98,0:15:26.23,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,您休息一会儿吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.07,0:15:28.07,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我说  十丸院
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.94,0:15:31.74,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,你再给他们涨点时薪吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.20,0:15:36.20,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我和姬约好了一起吃午饭
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.20,0:15:42.00,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,这是我在店里做的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.67,0:15:44.46,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,看上去玩得很开心嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.96,0:15:47.17,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我可是严格把控品质了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.92,0:15:49.63,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,除此之外还体验了什么工作呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.34,0:15:53.18,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,糕点师  快递员
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.59,0:15:54.89,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,还有警察
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.64,0:15:58.31,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我好想一直这样下去
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.81,0:16:01.14,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,老师  快到下午的时间了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.77,0:16:03.73,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,赶快点
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.94,0:16:06.90,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,老师  您在干什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.56,0:16:07.94,kakushigoto in 8,,0,0,0,,{\bord3\c&H2C3842&\3c&HD7E6E9&\pos(704,16)}戒潟魁吏的世界展
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.48,0:16:10.19,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我听说这次在画展在上野举办
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.82,0:16:11.61,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,你认识吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.11,0:16:14.24,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,这人可是日本画界的大家啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.07,0:16:18.78,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我超级喜欢这人的画  很敬仰他
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.70,0:16:22.58,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,居然是这么厉害的一个人物啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.50,0:16:26.29,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我家里有一幅  下次要不给你看看
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.83,0:16:28.38,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,老师您又在开玩笑了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.55,0:16:31.38,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,绘画大师啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.26,0:16:33.59,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,同是画画的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.80,0:16:35.18,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,和画连环画的我相比
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.43,0:16:36.64,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,真是云泥之别啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.72,0:16:40.47,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,太慢了  老师
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.89,0:16:42.10,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,还要继续吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.77,0:16:44.85,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,这种事情对谁都没好处
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.14,0:16:47.44,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我明白老师您刚才说的意思了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.94,0:16:50.36,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,他们怎么可能是来打工的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.82,0:16:52.53,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,你有证据吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.15,0:16:55.03,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,就老师您签售会挣来的那点钱
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.03,0:16:57.66,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,还不够支付托儿们的工资呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.20,0:17:00.53,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,「就」是什么意思啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.04,0:17:04.50,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,真不知道您的职业尊严到底还在不在
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.12,0:17:06.21,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,老师您看看这些
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.58,0:17:08.75,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,都是粉丝送来的信和礼物
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.34,0:17:11.21,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,您觉得打工的可能做到这个地步吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.76,0:17:15.30,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,他们可是真的喜欢老师您的漫画
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.84,0:17:17.26,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,您稍微对自己有些自信啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.09,0:17:19.97,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,下午的签售会开始了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.81,0:17:25.06,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,谢谢您
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.48,0:17:27.94,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,虽然我还是有些难以相信
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.81,0:17:30.65,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,这群人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.77,0:17:32.48,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,全都…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.95,0:17:39.91,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,读过我的漫画
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.08,0:17:42.79,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,但这还不能够告诉姬
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.58,0:17:44.54,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,拜托您了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.21,0:17:50.58,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,看起来您是带着小孩子来的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.79,0:17:52.80,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,他知道我画的是什么吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.92,0:17:54.96,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我画的可是黄色段子哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.46,0:17:56.63,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,他当然知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.43,0:17:58.55,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我们父子俩都是您的粉丝
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.76,0:18:05.52,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,爸爸  紧身裤诶
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.73,0:18:06.52,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.98,0:18:08.98,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,{\an8}你可要好好保管它哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.60,0:18:08.60,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,好棒
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.73,0:18:12.02,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,所以我才叫您稍微对自己有些信心
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.69,0:18:15.15,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,您看  就连那么小的孩子也是您的粉丝
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.78,0:18:19.20,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,真的是  就连那么小的孩子…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.07,0:18:22.62,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,要是雇佣了  可就是违反法律了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.87,0:18:23.58,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,你指这个啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.70,0:18:25.58,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,也没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.12,0:18:28.37,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我只是为我相信的漫画而画而已
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.83,0:18:30.62,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.33,0:18:33.50,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,他好像重新拾起信心了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.50,0:18:37.30,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,无论绘画大师怎么对我说三道四
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.13,0:18:40.89,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我的职业就是漫画家
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.48,0:18:54.94,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,被…被发现了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.78,0:18:59.11,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,赶快换人  轮到我了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.36,0:19:03.57,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,老师  您在干什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.12,0:19:06.12,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我在体…体验工作哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.62,0:19:09.54,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,原来这里是大人们的Kidzanira
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.12,0:19:11.79,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,就是这么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.29,0:19:14.67,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,毕竟大人们在等待的时候很无聊嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.55,0:19:21.01,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我还得去找爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.26,0:19:25.76,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,爸爸到了约好的时间还没来  一定是迷路了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.60,0:19:29.60,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,是和家里的打扮出入太大
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.60,0:19:32.27,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,所以没能认出您来是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.94,0:19:35.82,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,您的漫画家COSPLAY第一次立功了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.11,0:19:37.40,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,这才不是COSPLAY
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.03,0:19:42.20,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,今天什么工作比较开心呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.07,0:19:45.66,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,全部都很开心
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.49,0:19:50.12,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,但最开心的还是当书店员工
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.67,0:19:55.17,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,真是  很辛苦的工作呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.92,0:19:56.84,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,但我真的很开心
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.34,0:20:00.26,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,爸爸给你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.97,0:20:01.80,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,这是送给你的礼物
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.13,0:20:04.22,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,你是从哪里得来的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.72,0:20:06.26,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我工作买来的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.10,0:20:09.68,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,工作？在Kidzanira工作得来的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.31,0:20:13.14,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,工作的话就能得到一种叫Kidz的钱
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.60,0:20:16.27,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,在那里就可以使用它购买东西
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.40,0:20:19.53,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,姬工作为我买来的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.28,0:20:23.03,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.95,0:20:27.03,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,但那个的门票一定很贵吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.87,0:20:31.29,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,毕竟是花了钱才让我工作的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.50,0:20:35.96,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,本来画画这工作
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.46,0:20:39.21,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,即使让我付钱我也愿意做下去
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.17,0:20:40.80,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,但不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.21,0:20:45.22,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我还能将这份工作做到多久
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.14,0:20:51.81,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,那个  大人版的Kidzanira也有工作介绍处吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.56,0:20:55.52,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,爸爸  你有去过吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.40,0:21:00.32,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,以后我可能会去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.28,0:21:08.95,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,那里有着箱子的后续
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.37,0:21:12.24,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,那些箱子
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.62,0:21:17.83,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,是爸爸为我准备的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.38,0:21:22.00,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,漫画？
