Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.59,0:21:25.22,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,那是一本
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.43,0:21:28.76,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,特别特别无趣的漫画
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.26,0:21:31.97,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,没有剑也没有魔法
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.02,0:21:34.52,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,没有任何的波澜起伏
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.85,0:21:36.39,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,只有
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.06,0:21:39.98,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,爸爸  妈妈  和女儿
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.02,0:21:44.28,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,一家三口平凡的生活故事
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.74,0:21:47.24,kakushigoto in 2,,0,0,0,,{\frz32.6\pos(1046,262)}17
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.74,0:21:47.24,kakushigoto in 2 - zong,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1138,280)\frz298.7}岁生日快乐
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.95,0:21:51.49,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,但这无趣的日常生活
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.74,0:21:56.96,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,才是最为梦幻的故事
